{"tid":2511233,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實食芒果根本唔撚使剝皮","createTime":"2021-04-30T18:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T21:16:25.000Z","uid":282619,"like":13,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"99493f52cf9cecb1b3792615264de0cf7c0f1a84","tid":2511233,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:08:05.000Z","msg":"剝皮食芒果就好似你飲汽水，但走冰而且唔要凍嘅汽水一樣，唔係話唔好飲，但硬係差啲嘢囉，浸皮就好似冰咁，屌你剝咗皮，無咗嗰個襯托，咁食乜撚嘢？唔係話唔好食，但你如果連皮食個層次會再升一級囉<br />\n你未試過連皮食一定話我戇撚尻，但我同你講，你連皮食過一次，包你食完食唔返轉頭，分分鐘仲想過嚟多謝我教你一個咁好食嘅食法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />剝皮食正戇尻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連皮食先係正道"},{"pid":"d3121c3632913c405d03aaf138530b7f76192193","tid":2511233,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:09:07.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"10e710e77356008e652dca5c5e128f5d6bdbd49d","tid":2511233,"uid":133364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:09:50.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"127db58e0365e589d9aedcd99ef89d4e808f931b","tid":2511233,"uid":308107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:10:32.000Z","msg":"你講得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe39e65d670fe7524ea2b7efa758371ca7a14e3","tid":2511233,"uid":370,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:11:04.000Z","msg":"負皮=樓主正on<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43d6a753c2e500e4b109732e20cbc087a2ef561","tid":2511233,"uid":174739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:12:37.000Z","msg":"你講得好岩,我食香蕉都係連皮食!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br 